The paper deals with the endowment effect in combinatorial markets, which is a topic in algorithmic game theory (cs.GT) and computational social choice (cs.EC). The paper also introduces a framework for capturing different types of endowment effects, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.AI) and optimization (cs.LG, cs.DS).
